        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Bit[0]: Multi-Lane (ML) Data Transfer Support</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Bit[1]: Device to Device Transfer (D2DXFER) Support</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Bit[2]: Device to Device Transfer (D2DXFER) IBI Capable</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Bit[3]: Defining Byte Support in GETCAPS</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Bit[4]: Defining Byte Support in GETSTATUS</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Bit[5]: HDR-BT CRC-32 Support</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Bit[6]: IBI MDB Support for Pending Read Notification</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Bit[7]: Reserved </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
